OL,5,G1720 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FNeil and Mary Blackburn welcome
OL,7,     Ftheir rivals to Fernie Castle in
OL,8,     FFife. There's plenty of
OL,9,     Ftraditional Scots splendour on
OL,10,     Fshow, but two guests aren't
OL,11,     Fimpressed by the continental
OL,12,     Fbreakfast.
OL,13,G1750 Four in a Bed
OL,14,     FThe last visit of the week is to
OL,15,     Fthe Cadillac Kustomz Hotel on the
OL,16,     FIsle of Bute, where owners Brody
OL,17,     Fand Rima hope to rock their
OL,18,     Fguests' worlds with a music-filled
OL,19,     Fretro retreat.
